com.google.api.client.http.javanet
Class NetHttpTransport

java.lang.Object
  com.google.api.client.http.HttpTransport
      com.google.api.client.http.javanet.NetHttpTransport

public final class NetHttpTransport
extends HttpTransport

Thread-safe HTTP low-level transport based on the java.net package.

Upgrade warning: prior version 1.3 had connectTimeout and readTimeout fields. Instead now use HttpRequest.connectTimeout and HttpRequest.readTimeout in an HttpRequestInitializer.

Since:
1.0
Author:
Yaniv Inbar
